{{Infobox musical artist | name = Alexandra Cardenas | background = non_vocal_instrumentalist | alias = | origin = Colombia | genre = [[Free improvisation]], [[Algorave]]| | occupation = | years_active = 2000–present | website = {{URL|http://cargocollective.com/tiemposdelruido}} }} '''Alexandra Cardenas''' (born 1976) is a Colombian composer and improviser<ref>{{Cite web|title = Navis fracta: de viaje entre la música y la escultura |language=Spanish |url = http://www.noticiasnet.mx/portal/oaxaca/141773-navis-fracta-viaje-entre-musica-escultura|website = Noticiasnet|access-date = 2016-01-21}}</ref> now based in Berlin, who has followed a path from Western classical composition to improvisation and live electronics .<ref>{{Cite web|title = Interview: Alexandra Cardenas |author=Alex |date=November 27, 2013 |publisher=[[TOPLAP]]|url = http://toplap.org/interview-alexandra-cardenas/|accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref> Her recent work has included [[live coding]] performance,<ref>{{Cite web |title=Live coding: le mariage geek des algorithmes et de la musique |first1=Elisabeth |last1=Debourse |url = http://focus.levif.be/culture/musique/live-coding-le-mariage-geek-des-algorithmes-et-de-la-musique/article-normal-12607.html|website = focus.levif.be|date = 2014-02-05|access-date = 2016-01-21}}</ref> including performances at the forefront of the [[Algorave]] scene,<ref>{{Cite web |date=29 August 2013 |first1=Tom |last1=Cheshire|title =Culture: Hacking meets clubbing with the 'algorave' |work=[[Wired UK]] |url = https://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2013/09/play/algorave|accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Hacking + Clubbing = Algorave!|url = http://www.arte.tv/de/hacking-clubbing-algorave/7769884,CmC=7768150.html|website = Arte TV|accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |first1=Florian |last1=Reynaud |title = Les programmeurs sont les nouveaux DJ|url = http://www.slate.fr/culture/77242/programmation-dj-musique-algorithme|publisher= Slate.fr |work=[[Slate (magazine)|Slate]]|access-date = 2016-01-21|language = fr-FR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = High Zero Festival of Experimental Improvised Music in Baltimore 2015 :: 17 Years!|url = http://www.highzero.org/2015_site/performers/|website = www.highzero.org|access-date = 2016-01-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.inka-magazin.de/clubkultur/algorave-2.html |work=[[Inka (magazine)|Inka]] |series=Algorave Clubkultur |date=November 14, 2015 |title=Alexandra Cardenas:Internationale Gäste beim dritten Karlsruher Algorave“! |language=German |accessdate=February 3, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.ndr.de/der_ndr/presse/mitteilungen/TOXIC-TUNES-neue-Konzertreihe-fuer-Hamburg-praesentiert-von-NDR-neue-werk,pressemeldungndr16488.html |date=November 16, 2015 |work=NDR |publisher=[[Norddeutscher Rundfunk]] |title="TOXIC TUNES" - neue Konzertreihe für Hamburg, präsentiert von NDR das neue werk Auftaktkonzert: Dienstag, 1. Dezember, 20.00 Uhr, Resonanzraum St. Pauli, Hamburg|accessdate=February 3, 2016 |language=German}}</ref> she also co-organised a live coding community in Mexico City. At the 2014 [[Kurukshetra (festival)|Kurukshetra Festival]] Cardenas was a keynote speaker and hosted a music live coding workshop, the first of its kind in India.<ref>{{Cite web|title = LIVE CODING {{!}} Kurukshetra 2014 {{!}} The Battle of Brains |location=[[Kurukshetra]]|url = http://www.archive14.kurukshetra.org.in/workshops/LIVECODING|website = Kurukshetra 2014 {{!}} The Battle of Brains|access-date = 2016-01-22|first = Chandresh|last = Rajkumar}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Algoraves: Dancing to live coding - SD Times|url = http://sdtimes.com/algoraves-dancing-to-live-coding/|accessdate = 2015-05-02}}</ref> Cardenas has been invited to talk about and perform live coding at events such as the Berlin based [[Transmediale]] festival<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ndr.de/orchester_chor/das_neue_werk/TOXIC-TUNES-Konzert-Nummer-1,firstnight100.html |language=German |title