'''Brooke Skye''' (born '''Hope Danielle Miller''',<ref name=CourtTV /> September 5, 1986<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mugshots.com/US-Counties/Florida/Lee-County-FL/Hope-Danielle-Miller.20077204.html |title=Hope Danielle Miller mugshot |accessdate=July 4, 2014}}</ref> in [[Plant City, Florida]]) is a model, and former [[United States|American]] [[pornographic actress]] who currently lives in [[San Diego, California]].

==Harassment lawsuit==
Skye has appeared on the radio program ''[[Bubba the Love Sponge Show]]'' three times. In October 2006, Miller sued host [[Bubba the Love Sponge|Todd Clem]] claiming that she was harassed and injured during an on-air stunt involving an oversized [[sex toy]] with porn actress [[Melissa Harrington]].<ref name=CourtTV>{{cite news |author=Emanuella Greenberg |title=Porn model claims radio host forced her into live sex act on his show |url=http://www.courttv.com/news/2006/1011/brooke_skye_ctv.html |publisher=[[Court TV]] |date=October 11, 2006 |accessdate=2008-03-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061018151959/http://www.courttv.com/news/2006/1011/brooke_skye_ctv.html |archivedate=2006-10-18}}</ref><ref name=upi>{{cite news |title=Shock jock Clem sued on botched sex stunt |url=http://www.upi.com/NewsTrack/Entertainment/2006/10/07/shock_jock_clem_sued_on_botched_sex_stunt/8032/ |publisher=United Press International |date=October 7, 2006 |accessdate=2008-03-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080118103033/http://www.upi.com/NewsTrack/Entertainment/2006/10/07/shock_jock_clem_sued_on_botched_sex_stunt/8032/ |archivedate=2008-01-18 |df= }}</ref> In 2007, a judge turned down a request by Clem's attorneys to dismiss the lawsuit, indicating that there was enough that Miller has a legitimate claim.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.heraldtribune.com/article/20070726/NEWS/707260465?p=1&tc=pg |title=Judge refuses to toss radio lawsuit |publisher=HeraldTribune.com |accessdate=2011-02-05 |date=2007-07-26 |author=Thomas W. Krause}}</ref> However, the case was eventually voluntarily dismissed with prejudice.<ref name=docket>{{cite news |title=Court Docket |url=http://publicrecord.hillsclerk.com/oridev/criminal_pack.doc?pcSearchMode=NS&pnPidm=5956261&pcCaseId=06-CA-009125&pnCnt=1&pcFirst=BUBBA&pcLast=CLEM&pcMi=THE%20LOVE%20SPONGE&pcSuf=&pcId=@5956091&pcByear=&pcPtyp=D003&pcDefStat=Closed%20-%2005/19/2008&pdInit=06-OCT-06&pcCaseStat=Closed%20-%2005/19/2008&pcCtyp=CD&pcLocn=TA&pcPref=&pcWarrant=&pcCaseDscr=CIVIL%20ACTION%20FOR%20DAMAGES&pcDiv=K&pcCourtType=&pnCaseYrFr=1970&pnCaseYrTo=2011&pcCtypCL=&pcLocnCL= |publisher= Hillsborough County Clerk of the Circuit Court |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711165900/http://publicrecord.hillsclerk.com/oridev/criminal_pack.doc?pcSearchMode=NS&pnPidm=5956261&pcCaseId=06-CA-009125&pnCnt=1&pcFirst=BUBBA&pcLast=CLEM&pcMi=THE%20LOVE%20SPONGE&pcSuf=&pcId=%405956091&pcByear=&pcPtyp=D003&pcDefStat=Closed%20-%2005%2F19%2F2008&pdInit=06-OCT-06&pcCaseStat=Closed%20-%2005%2F19%2F2008&pcCtyp=CD&pcLocn=TA&pcPref=&pcWarrant=&pcCaseDscr=CIVIL%20ACTION%20FOR%20DAMAGES&pcDiv=K&pcCourtType=&pnCaseYrFr=1970&pnCaseYrTo=2011&pcCtypCL=&pcLocnCL= |archivedate=2011-07-11 |df= }}</ref>

